data.description: Beautiful, sophisticated Luxury living in a privately gated townhome community. Great color scheme and tile flooring throughout. Beautiful kitchen with breakfast granite countertop and stainless appliances. A spacious living and dining areas. Second floor features all bedrooms with 2 full baths and bonus room perfect for a study or entertainment. Scenic landscaping and pool for entertaining.   This luxurious townhouse is located just south of Trenton Rd on 2nd Street and is minutes away from DHR Hospital, HEB, Home Depot and tons of restaurants and banks.
